[4:46 PM] Eve: Hello and welcome! I'm Eve, your AI assistant. I'm here to support you through a psycho-oncology assessment, which helps us understand your mental wellbeing as you navigate your cancer journey. It's an important part of your healing process. Shall we begin?

[4:47 PM] Patient: My family has been very supportive during this difficult time

[4:47 PM] Eve: It's wonderful to hear that your family has been a strong support for you. Having a supportive network can make a big difference. Let's talk a bit more about your experience. How have you been feeling about your treatment lately?

[4:47 PM] Patient: I'm struggling with fatigue most days

[4:47 PM] Eve: I'm sorry to hear that fatigue has been a challenge for you. It's a common side effect and can be tough to manage. How has this impacted your mood and daily activities?
